Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.76,0:00:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Trebor1号呼叫飞龙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.04,0:00:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是飞龙  怎么了
