Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.63,0:00:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大型移动物体？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.88,0:00:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法通过IRUO.进行情报搜索操作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推测其长度超过15米
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.39,0:00:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管它
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.24,0:00:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按照预定计划  Trebor继续原地待命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.21,0:00:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,专心准备发射
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.23,0:01:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离发射还有47分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.89,0:01:06.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,液体燃料准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.45,0:01:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风速1.0  无降水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.42,0:01:14.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大型移动物体即将抵达发射场
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.37,0:01:17.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,申请发射导弹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.21,0:01:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞龙呼叫Trebor
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否使用导弹由我来决定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.48,0:01:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要离开工作岗位
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.92,0:01:34.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.55,0:01:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美纱姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.75,0:01:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.09,0:01:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.20,0:01:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
