Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.20,0:03:40.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AR诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,启动！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.86,0:03:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哇…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.89,0:03:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这就是战场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.74,0:03:58.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  真不愧是泽田亲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.18,0:04:01.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.66,0:04:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.96,0:04:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来AR诱饵好像起作用了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.38,0:04:10.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导弹无效的话就没什么好怕的了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一口气逼近吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:15.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  并不是所有的导弹都被无效化了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.26,0:04:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AR诱饵通过干扰IRUO.  来使对方将AR误认为本体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:24.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使其难以击中本体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:26.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是类似于分身术一般的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然几率很低
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.01,0:04:33.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还是有可能偶然命中本体的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.26,0:04:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.43,0:04:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小亚希  按下按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.22,0:04:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.20,0:05:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打桩机…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.35,0:05:26.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右手的还能用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.70,0:05:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要跑吗  美纱姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.53,0:05:41.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,SUMERAGI正与大型移动物体交战中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.31,0:05:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火箭一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.58,0:05:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续进行发射倒计时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.29,0:05:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一有破绽我就冲过去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.85,0:05:49.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请掩护我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.34,0:05:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.88,0:05:55.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还剩30分钟…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.61,0:06:09.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离这么近的话  你就没法发射导弹了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧  美纱姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.06,0:06:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.31,0:06:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.91,0:06:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:47.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那机体可是我进行调整的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.78,0:06:55.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怒吼吧！磁单极子驱动器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.13,0:07:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.32,0:07:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.10,0:07:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小亚希
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:31.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gunvarrel十字火箭拳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒它了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.15,0:07:55.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.44,0:07:57.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的摄像机应该已经被破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.65,0:07:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:03.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美纱姐  你听得到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.43,0:08:07.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.86,0:08:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来向小亚希…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲口向小亚希解释一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.64,0:08:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么放弃了Gun制造计划
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要说出那种话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:21.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你全都要给我解释清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了听你的解释
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.91,0:08:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小亚希一路追了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.80,0:08:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并追上了你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.88,0:08:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.64,0:08:32.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要逃避啊  美纱姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:39.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼哼哼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.38,0:08:42.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真遗憾  你迟了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.14,0:08:46.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的意识已经崩溃了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我将其沉入了黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.89,0:08:50.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自爆？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.60,0:09:14.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是个没有自我意识的牵线木偶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而操纵她的人正是我君岛晃
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:33.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,君岛…晃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是B小组
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.54,0:09:37.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已成功夺回控制室
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来开始停止火箭发射
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.29,0:09:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.69,0:09:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火箭的发射是不会停下的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:46.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我必须要让实验成功
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.84,0:10:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.57,0:10:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:19.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜…呜哇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我死了  真的死了  刚刚死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.22,0:10:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但接下来只能靠内部电池了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.77,0:10:47.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,运转时间大约为5分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:52.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小亚希穗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:53.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:56.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管尝试多少次  火箭都不接受发射中止命令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:10:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命令被管理员拦截了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:03.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的管理员是…君岛晃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.59,0:11:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼哼哼  这实验可是赌上了这么长的时间和我的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要让它成功
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.40,0:11:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:25.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.32,0:11:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来来来…来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:30.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泽田亲  ktkr
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神代同学  这时候还是别开玩笑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.30,0:11:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:35.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,程序发过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.87,0:11:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够删除掉君岛晃的程序
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.94,0:11:38.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.17,0:11:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要使用的话  需先进行安装
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.24,0:11:47.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后让君岛的AR出现在口袋本的画面上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并将其锁定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,0:11:51.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在此之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.43,0:11:56.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安装需要重启口袋本
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.27,0:12:00.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重启？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.08,0:12:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.17,0:12:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后还要想尽办法把姐姐从驾驶舱里弄出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.59,0:12:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话就一定能捕捉到君岛晃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.40,0:12:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可别注意到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:35.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还剩10分钟…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.09,0:12:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通信完全切断了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.83,0:12:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是在做些什么小动作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没反应吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.11,0:13:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.33,0:13:02.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.41,0:13:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长  八汐学长正在重启口袋本
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.09,0:13:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他完全看不到对方的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.53,0:13:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.54,0:13:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.91,0:13:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.17,0:13:28.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:30.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.96,0:13:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快停下  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.47,0:13:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.77,0:13:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是亚希啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.07,0:13:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.74,0:13:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.93,0:13:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说她居然还有自我意识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小亚希  快退后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.41,0:14:06.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊  美纱姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:09.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊  放马过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美纱姐你应该不是那种会在电视上点头哈腰的和蔼类型吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而应该是能够若无其事地取得完全胜利的无情女人  对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:20.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.37,0:14:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明是个女孩子  却喜欢机器人动画
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.77,0:14:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种乡下居然还真心想着要造什么巨型机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:30.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后还把周围的人全都拉下水  你不是这种笨女人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.56,0:14:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(439,325)\fs16}Right Stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.56,0:14:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的你  还有只属于自己的正确资质吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.26,0:14:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我啊  美纱姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是再这么大放厥词的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.64,0:14:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就灭了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.35,0:14:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  接下来的游戏是属于我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.92,0:14:56.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是知道的  美纱姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:14:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你玩「Kiilballad」的时候也总是这样出招
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.28,0:15:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小亚希！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.75,0:15:16.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面对美纱姐  我一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.17,0:15:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往右躲四帧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.59,0:15:59.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.15,0:16:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.18,0:16:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很遗憾  但美纱希已经消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:08.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:09.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.70,0:16:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是Gun制造1号机哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.47,0:16:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是姐姐你曾经一直在制造的机器人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:18.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来这里就是为了说这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.81,0:16:22.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是凝聚了姐姐和我还有大家的思念的机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.37,0:16:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它在动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.03,0:16:27.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它正打算去拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你们姐妹俩都有惊人的精神力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.51,0:16:43.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸他第一次给我看机器人的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐你是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.80,0:16:51.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我喜欢机器人！  喜欢它胜过这世上的一切！」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:57.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在  你还喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.81,0:17:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  你现在还喜欢机器人胜过这世上的一切吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.49,0:17:07.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.25,0:17:37.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明  明明就只差一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:38.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:44.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过总有一天  还会有第二个  第三个我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:45.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.07,0:17:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  就算这样正义似乎还是总会取得胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:56.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的部长是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.96,0:18:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许她说的对…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:27.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚希
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.11,0:18:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.18,0:18:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已从君岛晃手上取得了管理员权限
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.75,0:18:45.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,输入停止命令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.26,0:18:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:02.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒计时停下了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.40,0:19:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们成功阻止了火箭的发射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:08.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来…来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功…好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲击力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波霸～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.31,0:19:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  这摇滚还真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.82,0:19:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.66,0:19:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.82,0:19:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小亚希
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.96,0:19:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美纱姐情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:30.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:32.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她只是晕过去了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.22,0:19:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海  我们回机库吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.67,0:21:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.74,0:21:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.72,0:21:28.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海你今后有什么打算？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.78,0:21:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后是指？
